《'''紅色覺醒'''》（{{lang-en|''Red Rising''}}）是2014年由美國作家[[皮爾斯·布朗|皮爾斯·布朗]]所寫的科幻小說，三部曲小說的第一本。小說設定在未來的[[火星|火星]]，出身低賤的礦工Darrow潛入金督（Golds）最高階層的故事。2014年2月，[[環球影業|環球影業]]獲得改編電影的版權，由[[馬克·福斯特|馬克·福斯特]]執導。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://deadline.com/2014/02/universal-wins-7-figure-auction-for-red-rising-with-marc-forster-helming-mars-tale-678707/ |title = Universal Wins 7-Figure Auction For 'Red Rising,' With Marc Forster Helming Mars Tale |author = Mike Fleming Jr |date = 2014-02-06 |publisher = Deadline Hollywood |language = en |access-date = 2016-11-28 |archive-date = 2021-02-11 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210211170833/https://deadline.com/2014/02/universal-wins-7-figure-auction-for-red-rising-with-marc-forster-helming-mars-tale-678707/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>

